title: Back from Vacation Vlog. Catching up with Jordan Peterson again
description:
I'm back from my vacation. Sorry I didn't make any videos for a week and am behind on comments and correspondence. Here are a variety of articles and videos that came out over the last week. 

Pt. 2 of Peterson's interview with the Swede where CS Lewis gets mentioned https://youtu.be/B74WowudoFg 

JBP: The Intellectual We Deserve in Current Affairs https://www.currentaffairs.org/2018/03/the-intellectual-we-deserve 

Bishop Barron talks Jordan Peterson Phenom https://youtu.be/Bm3nVTF90mw 

David French on JBP in National Review https://www.nationalreview.com/magazine/2018/03/01/jordan-peterson-12-rules-for-life-book-times/ 

Andrew Sullivan on Pinker vs. Deneen http://nymag.com/daily/intelligencer/2018/03/sullivan-things-are-better-than-ever-why-are-we-miserable.html 

JBP in First Things https://www.firstthings.com/article/2018/04/jordan-peterson-unlikely-guru 

JBP Melbourne Speech audio https://soundcloud.com/user-207957139/jordan-peterson-melbourne-speech 

JBP in The Gospel Coalition by Joe Carter
